<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .notice {
      background-color: #fee2e2;
      border-left: 4px solid #ef4444;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background-color: #2563eb;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #6b7280;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1 style="color: #1f2937; margin: 0;">Property Listing Update</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello <%= firstName %>,</p>
      
      <p>Thank you for submitting your property listing to our platform. After careful review, we're unable to approve your listing at this time.</p>
      
      <div class="notice">
        <p style="font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 4px;">Reason for Rejection:</p>
        <p style="margin-top: 0;"><%= rejectionReason %></p>
      </div>
      
      <p>You can edit your listing to address these issues and resubmit it for review:</p>
      
      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="<%= appUrl %>/properties/edit/<%= propertyId %>" class="button">
          Edit Your Listing
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
      
      <p>
        Best regards,<br>
        The GetOnePlot Team
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; <%= year %> GetOnePlot. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>